title: "Figure 4 — Experiment Execution Sub-Process (general · drawn by Claude)"
---
flowchart LR
    Cfg[Experiment spec<br/>(declarative artifact:<br/>YAML / JSON / TOML)] --> Launcher[Experiment launcher<br/>(thin shell wrapper)]
    Launcher --> Pre[Pre-flight checks:<br/>resource selection +<br/>capacity validation +<br/>output-path policy]
    Pre --> Init[Pipeline init:<br/>seed / logging / metrics sink]
    Init --> Data[Data layer<br/>(load, split, batch)]
    Init --> Core[Core component A<br/>(always-on backbone)]
    Init --> CoreB[Core component B<br/>(always-on head)]

    Core --> Feat[Primary representation]
    CoreB --> Repr[Representation refinement]

    Feat --> ObjMain[Main objective term<br/>(always present)]
    Repr -.-> ObjMain

    Feat --> OptA{Optional module A<br/>(ablation switch)}
    OptA -- on --> OptAOn[Module A active]
    OptA -- off --> OptAOff[Module A skipped]
    OptAOn --> ObjA[Auxiliary objective A]

    OptAOn --> OptB{Optional module B<br/>(REQUIRES A)}
    OptB -- on --> OptBOn[Module B active]
    OptB -- off --> OptBOff[Module B skipped]
    OptBOn --> ObjB[Auxiliary objective B]

    OptAOn --> OptC{Optional module C<br/>(REQUIRES A)}
    OptC -- on --> OptCOn[Module C active]
    OptC -- off --> OptCOff[Module C skipped]
    OptCOn --> ObjC[Auxiliary objective C]

    Repr --> OptD{Optional module D<br/>(INDEPENDENT)}
    OptD -- on --> OptDOn[Module D active]
    OptD -- off --> OptDOff[Module D skipped]
    OptDOn --> ObjD[Auxiliary objective D]

    ObjMain --> Sum[Composite objective<br/>= weighted sum of active terms]
    ObjA --> Sum
    ObjB --> Sum
    ObjC --> Sum
    ObjD --> Sum

    Sum --> Step[Optimization step]
    Step --> Eval[Periodic evaluation<br/>(per-checkpoint metrics<br/>+ search-space sweeps)]
    Eval --> Track[Best-tracker<br/>(maintains running optimum)]
    Track --> Save[Persist checkpoints:<br/>best-by-metric +<br/>final state +<br/>metric snapshot]
    Save --> Finish[Write FINISH-line to log<br/>(authoritative end signal<br/>read by reaper in Figure 1)]

